language ESSENCE 1.2.0

given v, b, r, k, lambda_ : int(1..)

where
    r * v = b * k,
    lambda_ * (v-1) = r * (k-1),
    b >= v

letting Obj   be new type of size v
letting Block be new type of size b

find bibd : relation of ( Obj * Block )

such that
    forAll o      : Obj   . |bibd(o,_)| = r,
    forAll bl     : Block . |bibd(_,bl)| = k,
    forAll o1, o2 : Obj   , o1 != o2
                          . |bibd(o1,_) intersect bibd(o2,_)| = lambda_
